**Summary:** This documentation covers the Amplitude Shopify Plugin that installs the Amplitude Browser SDK with Session Replay and Web Experiment capabilities, automatically tracking Shopify standard events (checkout, cart, product views) and Amplitude default events with marketing attribution, while addressing Shopify-specific limitations like checkout page restrictions and flickering issues.

